headline: Duke Energy kicks off monthlong campaign providing more than $500,000 to help fight hunger in South Carolina
summary: Every community in South Carolina is home to families who face hunger. The statistics are startling – nearly 700,000 of our friends and neighbors lack consistent access to high-quality meals. That's 1 in 8 people facing hunger in our state every day, and 1 in 6 of those are children.
